body.description: The Flash Ultimate Figure Set is a must-have for DC fans! Speed into action with this Amazon Exclusive, featuring 5 iconic characters: The Flash, Batman, The Flash Young Barry, General Zod and Supergirl. When you’re ready to battle, gear up your action figures with the included 10 accessories and recreate your favorite scenes from The Flash movie! The Flash movie action figures are highly detailed with 11 points of articulation for dynamic battle stances. Team up your favorite Super Heroes against General Zod! Zoom off with The Flash to defend the world against chaos! With a detailed sculpt and awesome movie-styling, your figures will come to life! Kids love to engage their imagination and create their own Super Hero scenes! With a range of cool toys for boys and girls to collect from The Flash movie, you can now expand your DC action figures with The Flash, Dark Flash, Batman action figure, and more (each sold separately). These toys for girls and boys gifts are perfect for kids that love Justice League collectible figurines, DC multiverse, Super Hero movies collectibles, RC cars, and more!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Flash Ultimate Figure Set Amazon Exclusive Collect all 5 iconic action figures from The Flash movie, including The Flash, Batman, The Flash Young Barry, General Zod and Supergirl! Each figure has its own unique accessories! Includes 5 Action Figures 10 Accessories

STORYTELLING AND CREATIVITY Kids love to recreate their favorite scenes from The Flash movie and use their imagination to create their own storylines with their favorite Super Heroes and Super-Villains. 5 FIGURES AND ACCESSORIES Each figure includes 2 unique accessories, such as speed force effects, blaster, and more! EASY TO POSE These highly detailed figures have 11-points of articulation, featuring a detailed sculpt and awesome movie-styling – as seen in The Flash movie!
GREAT GIFT FOR DC FANS Inspired by the DC Universe, The Flash Ultimate Figure Set is the perfect gift for DC fans as a birthday, holiday, or surprise toy!

The Flash Ultimate Figure Set Speed Force The Flash Action Figure The Flash Ultimate Batwing Set The Flash Batwing Battle Set 1989 Batmobile RC The Flash Hero Set, Iconic Mask with Visor and Ring AGE 3+ 4+ 3+ 3+ 14+ 4+ ABOUT Collect all 5 action figures from The Flash in this Amazon Exclusive, including The Flash, Batman, The Flash Young Barry, General Zod and Supergirl! The 12-inch Speed Force The Flash action figure comes with full armor and lightning speed action features! Open up the cockpit and place The Flash and Batman into the epic Batwing vehicle. Pull up the landing gear and get defend the world against chaos! The Flash Batwing Battle Set is a must-have for DC fans – featuring The Flash, Supergirl, and an exclusive Nam-Ek. Team up the iconic heroes and take down enemies! The limited edition 1989 Batmobile RC comes to life with dynamic light-up headlights, water-activated smoke effects! Suit up as the fastest kid on earth with The Flash Hero Set, including an iconic light-up The Flash mask and ring! INCLUDES 5 Figures with Accessories 1 Speed Force The Flash Figure 2 Figures, Batwing 3 Figures, Batwing 1 Batmobile RC, 1 Charging Base, 1 4-inch Batman Figure, 1 Water Dropper, 2 AAA Batteries The Flash Mask, The Flash Ring

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This has the exclusive Nam-Ek figure, I had to have it.
reviews.reviewText: There are a few sets that have different figures with different vehicles, this one has the first Nam-Ek figures that I can remember seeing. If you are a Superman/Man of Steel fan, I would recommend this set with the figures. I enjoyed the movie too and had to have the Batplane as I like Michael Keaton's Batman too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great figure set
reviews.reviewText: Great figure, and perfect size for the Batwing, only thing makes it not perfect was the set doesn’t come with Batman figure, but easy to get one form the line

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing and a must buy
reviews.reviewText: Spin masters is killing it. Amazing quality especially for the price. The negative comments being left do not realize this is aimed at kids and yes, grown ups are buying them but you cannot expect McFarlane quality sculpts for a line aimed at kids and for the price. Be real.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Spin Master and female figures
reviews.reviewText: I actually I’m very pleased with the set. To finally have a better articulated movie Zod than the one released back in the day, is always welcome. Batman and the 2 Flash figures are very nice as well. All 5 could use torso articulation though. But this Supergirl (and Cylone from Black Adam, sorry but need a comparison) figure is an action figure that I would never buy as a single action figure. This is the type of quality for an action figure that a kid leaves at their grandparents house on purpose.

reviews.reviewText: Awesome item. Packaging was great. Delivered really fast.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Toy or collectible?
reviews.reviewText: My major concern was the condition of the packaging of the item. It looked as if a heavier package had been set on top of it. There were creases, scuffs and a puncture where an item inside had penetrated the box. The items inside were not damaged but bought as a collectible, the packaging was in at most fair condition.

reviews.reviewTitle: Único lugar donde puedes conseguir una figura de el villano de la película!
reviews.reviewText: El detalle es precioso. La escala pequeña lo hace más pr coleccionistas que para niños, pero si eres fan de DC, Flash, Batman, Superman o Superchica… que esperas? Está increÍble este set! incluye: Batman de Michael Keaton, Flash joven (uniforme de Batman modificado), Flash ruco, Supergirl de un universo alterno que le pusieron todo el fleco sobrecrecido en la cara (no soy fan de ese look pandroso, perdón) y el villano de la película: General Zod. Este es el único lugar donde puedes conseguir a Zod entonces olvídate de comprar individuales los monitos. Vete por este set. Las articulaciones están fuertes, tiesas por lo que puedes poner a tus monitos en poses de acción. Hubieran estado bien bases para pararlos en dichas poses. Increíble set. Ya. Convéncete y cómpralo.
De acuerdo al tamaño, marca , calidad y precio es un buen producto.

Conseguí este producto con descuento y lo compre me llego el día esperado y todo venía bien las figuras buenas aunque los puntos de articulación parece que se podrán flojos fácilmente pero de momento ningún problema

En general todas las figuras me gustan y me agrada que vengan cada uno con sus accesorios pero zod..... me decepciono mucho, tiene mucho nivel de detalle pero las hombreras le quitan toda la movilidad a los brazos . 7/10
Gran Set sobre todo por la figura del lacayo de Zod. La Bat Wing está bien bonita
